                Cohere, Mistral &mdash; plus OpenRouter, Together,
                Groq, DeepSeek, Fireworks, xAI, Perplexity, Cerebras
                via the OpenAI-compatible path.
              </p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">EMB</div>
              <h3>9 embedding providers</h3>
              <p>
                OpenAI, Azure, Bedrock (Titan + Cohere), Vertex,
                Gemini, Cohere, Mistral, Together, and
                <strong>Voyage AI</strong> &mdash; the canonical
                pairing for Anthropic Claude.
              </p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">TTS</div>
              <h3>5 text-to-speech providers</h3>
              <p>
                OpenAI <code>tts-1</code> / <code>tts-1-hd</code>,
                Azure, Gemini, <strong>ElevenLabs</strong> for highest
                quality, and <strong>Cartesia Sonic-2</strong> for
                sub-100 ms latency real-time agents.
              </p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">STT</div>
              <h3>5 speech-to-text providers</h3>
              <p>
                OpenAI Whisper, Azure Whisper, Groq Whisper, Gemini
