                and <strong>Deepgram Nova-3</strong> for per-word
                timing and diarization.
              </p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">URL</div>
              <h3>Any OpenAI-compatible endpoint</h3>
              <p>
                One <code>WithBaseURL</code> call points the OpenAI
                provider at OpenRouter, Together, Groq, vLLM, Ollama,
                LM Studio, or your private model behind a firewall.
                No new SDK per vendor.
              </p>
            </article>
            <article class="feature-card">
              <div class="feature-icon">A2</div>
              <h3>Apache-2.0, pre-1.0</h3>
              <p>
                Apache-2.0 licensed. Currently v0.3.x &mdash; expect
                minor API churn between minor versions until v1.0
                freezes the surface. Patch versions never break the
                API.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
